data.description: *** AWESOME PRICE IMPROVEMENT *** Welcome Home to Heron Bay Golf & Country Club, south Atlanta's premiere resort-style community. This spectacular home features an open concept with Master on the main!! Master bath features an en-suite with stand-alone soaking tub and separate shower. This awesome two-story front brick home boasts 5 BR and 3.5 BA with custom trim package, designer kitchen, stainless steel appliances, 42" cabinets, kitchen island, granite counter tops, hardwood floors, and a second living area upstairs with a mounted 70" tv that stays with the sale of the home. HUGE BONUS **The HOA cuts your grass and maintains your lawn** Heron Bay offers an unbelievable amenities package, including the Aquatic Center with zero entry pool with rain shower mushrooms, dual slides with splash pool, and a Jr. Olympic swimming pool! AND there's a second swim/tennis complex more centrally located in the community. Miles of nature trails. There's also the Lakefront Park and pavilion located on the 1100-acre Cole Reservoir --just perfect for kayaking, canoeing, paddle boats, fishing boats with trolling motors, and any non-gas watercraft! Social events throughout the year -- Make Heron Bay YOUR community! What are you waiting on...this one will not last long!!! Set up your appt today via Showingtime. Call me at 678-478-8927 if you have any questions.
